title: Hunks in Heels returns next week
text: Hunks in Heels returns next week Hunks in Heels returns next week File photo -- Ty Hingle at last year's Hunks in Heels. Photo provided by Racheal Hebert -- Artist Raina Wirta created flame-shooting heels with lights for Lieutenant Don Stone to wear in the Hunks in Heels show that benefits the Sexual Trauma Awareness and Response organization. Advocate file photo by Pam Bordelon -- Hunks Tracy Donovan Smith, left, and Ryan Chenevert pose with their artist-created heels at STAR's Hunks in Heels runway show. Advocate file photo by Pam Bordelon -- Barrinton Neil won the award for Hunkiest Heart at last year's STAR's Hunks in Heels runway show. Advocate file photo by Pam Bordelon -- Ryan Chenevert was proclaimed Easiest on the Eyes at last year's STAR's Hunks in Heels runway show. Kyle Peveto | kpeveto@theadvocate.com
